Quote: There are axes too - Eddie is a competitive axeman and attends around 20 chops each season. Not just to compete, but to keep in touch with the many axemen who use axes he has ground or, these days, that have been crafted in his workship. ... Sometimes he'll return from a chop with as many as 40 in the boot of his car for re-grinding.
